# ── Heavy data — NOT committed. Provided as a separate bundle (see DATA.md) ───
# The repo keeps code, notebooks, figures, docs, scenario sources, and trained
# models. Raw data + large derived CSVs are regenerated by the pipeline from the
# downloadable raw-data bundle. This keeps the repo ~43 MB.

# The data bundle zip itself (built for the GitHub Release, never committed)
ndn-data-bundle.zip
*.zip

# Raw data (the simulation/emulation source — in the bundle)
NDNsim/ndnsim-research-main/ndn-research/results/
miniNDN/Datacard/Logs/

# Large derived feature CSVs (regenerated by 01_preprocessing / the notebooks).
# Tiny result tables (ks_results, detection_latency) are kept for reference.
NDNsim/processed/*.csv
!NDNsim/processed/ks_results.csv
!NDNsim/processed/detection_latency.csv
miniNDN/Datacard/Datasets/*.csv
